  "texts": [
    "This arrangement enables researchers and developers to closely interact with patients and stakeholders, facilitating active participation, feedback, and iterative refinement of the VRehab platform 76, 77.",
    "Usability, acceptability, and safety.",
    "There is no validated scale available to measure the usability, acceptability, and safety of VRehab platforms.",
    "Commonly used scales to measure people's perceived usability of digital systems, such as the System Usability Scale 78, 79 are not tailored to VRehab platforms or patient populations and were designed for general use.",
    "Consequently, researchers have developed a variety of evaluation scales specific to their platforms 56, 57, 60, 62, 63."
  ],
